ygData.messageBody:
>From: "Sirenia" <paladin@...>
>Anyway, by my count there will be 3 of us on the new server so far...
Kyte, Lonewolf, and now my character... which will most likely be named
"Fraser". If there is anyone else coming to Brell Serilis, please let me
know your name and I will try to meet you on-line. My character class,
race, and name may change depending on what our needs are. But I truly hope
that we all can find our way to the unity we seek in each other somehow.
Regardless, good luck to all of you no matter where your journey leads you
in Norrath.


Just started Brieh in the high elf country on Brell. Haven't spent much
time yet. Still lvl 1.

B
